Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't dropping out a bit much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't we just start after graduating?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't the live house manager already tell us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lots of people waste their opportunities like that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just because they hesitate too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, but what about our parents?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't we just take a gap year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ooh, that might work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can just go back to school after finishing our album. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's no good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trust me, we'll make it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You heard the agency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're in the middle of a girls band revolution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we come to Tokyo, we'll definitely be a hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And they'll be backing us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think it's going to be that easy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Agreed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They didn't tell us to drop out of school, did they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, but I still want to bet everything on this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's some confidence there...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we make an escape route, we'll\ndefinitely want to use it at some point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having an escape route means we'll\nhave somewhere to look other than forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why we shouldn't give ourselves any way out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Momoka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, wait for us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}AIM FOR THE BUDOKAN!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to make it, I'm telling you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo…does anyone need a bathroom break?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you a question, Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You little-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t provoke her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that bathroom break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Start by apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:35.61,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H0FFFFFF&\3c&H777777&\4c&HFFFFFF\i1\b1\fnSegoe Script\pos(1450,932)}IF YOU WERE TO CRY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're on her side now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that outburst was entirely your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The stage is a place to communicate with the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a place for you to vent about everything that's wrong with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was the only place I could get you to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...there are other people here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not off the hook either. Why didn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? There's no way I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing. I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We should see where this goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this is all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My{\i0} fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You just decided to quit out of nowhere, without talking to us or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from the girl that sprung the whole pro thing on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are kinda in the wrong, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't {\i1}you{\i0} the one who stirred\nthis whole thing up in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I humbly apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, be all gung-ho about it like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll regret it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even understand how popular Diamond Dust are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn’t mean we should give up before even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to end up having to admit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that we were in the wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one avoiding reality, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you even know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me. Why did you keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think your music isn't enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you just call it quits and go back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why start a new band?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you shouldn’t drop out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, do what you want then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry for the disturbance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're acting! We're in the middle of filming for a TV show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Passionate, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd label that as "stupid".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to hit me, go ahead. I’m used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I want you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll finally give me a reason to hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you'll be just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Need some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for bringing me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in touch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I thought I was gonna suffocate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that guitar come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it when we were leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine-san gave her one of her spare guitars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your voice is raw and genuine, like Momoka's. I'll be cheering for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told the owner you’d bring back the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get off here too then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a pain, won't it?\nThere's lots of traffic where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The trains are still running, so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to take something\nfor your motion sickness next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you soon.\N- Drive safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are trains still running at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought a talk would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to be considerate, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of nice here. Pretty relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should move in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know if my roommate moves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Being roommates with you, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Rupa and Tomo know what Nina was planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But they probably weren’t too surprised,\nconsidering how Nina was acting lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re the only one who\ndidn't notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand how reckless this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven’t even released any music yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But we passed the selection for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rupa-san got offers from labels before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It might sound crazy to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but remember, you were a part of Diamond Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Rupa-san and Tomo-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they’re supposedly some kind\N of famous mysterious duo online.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And to top it off, a while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain singer tweeted that she liked Nina’s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And it got people talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, we gained a ton of followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And based on the festival's feedback survey, we have the largest amount of people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,coming to see us specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina isn’t completely\ndisconnected from reality, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe beating Diamond Dust is a bit much for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can at least take our first step towards that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Rupa and Tomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanted to go pro in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing’s for sure though,\nwe’re not going to be young forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out everyone was on the same page, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's like Nina always says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're serious, we need to cut off our escape routes and set concrete goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That’s why we shouldn't give ourselves any way out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ummm...this one, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A Minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,F.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,G.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How the heck do people do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Freedom, freedom, from now on I'm free!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow and the day after I’ll do what I want!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jakkajan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Dad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for raising me until now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on, I’ll try\nmy best to make it on my own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be needing money anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm returning my bankbook.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Muneo Iseri{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Step right up, step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we, a sushi place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say hello like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here a million times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't really pay attention to this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're a customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Put those thoughts into action and you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, why did you have to work {\i1}here{\i0} of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s my first job, so I thought\nit'd be nicer with someone I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking too damn long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We asked for the bill ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you even from, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cocky for a foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry. It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I need to be more "rock" too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check the stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what happened with Momoka in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we try to talk now it'll\ndefinitely turn into a fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying, if this goes on for much longer, we’re out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, step right u-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One medium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a beer with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to order something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some time after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can conclude that there was no bullying or harmful intent involved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a small incident that escalated a bit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can we leave it at that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I want both of you to submit your apology letters,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and end things on a good note with a handshake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iseri-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere close by. We'll be there in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to go somewhere in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thought it would be nice to drive\nwith you like this for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They could at least give us an update or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite of love is indifference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If they still want to talk after fighting so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's basically proof of their affection for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More like proof of their stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where you wanted to take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I rely on to guide myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just need to follow the manual of common sense{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And all its meaningless words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Days pass and are all the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what trying to survive after\ncutting off your escape routes looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room for luxuries like\nmaking the kind of music you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To survive, we constantly have to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of music is going to sell? What can\nget people talking? What's the optimal choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And chase those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not always true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing what they truly love
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is something very few artists can boast about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}YEAH, I'M NOT THEIR FAN ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}FAKE AS HELL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The original Diamond Dust members
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE VOCALIST SUCKS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE DD I KNOW IS DEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,didn’t want to go down that path either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE BAND'S GARBAGE WITHOUT MOMOKA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the choice they made to ensure their survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but that still doesn't mean\nyour music won't resonate with a wider audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your song rejected once,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and left the band without even trying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But they found a wider audience as they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, they were adamant about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"An idol band? Yeah right."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"We’ll make it with our own music, just watch us."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But the higher-ups weren't having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And sure, technically,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,critics loved us. But we weren’t profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our commercial songs were the\nonly ones that ended up being hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s how this world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You start to feel more and more pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the end, you're forced to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And only one choice allows you move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They made that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something you can blame them for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don’t want you to make the same choice I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me why I formed a band again\ninstead of going back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard you sing back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw myself in my early days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn’t care about money or success.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just singing what you loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the past me that I had loved so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The me that I no longer was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why I wanted you to sing as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Free from any constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be able to listen to you over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are Diamond Dust!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make some noise for the next band too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about my feelings in all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever stop to think how I'd feel about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a person, not a memory of your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't trap me in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright, now shake hands and make up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I rely on to guide myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iseri-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iseri-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina, wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is so white{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is so slow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the answers are empty of substance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if your fingers are trembling…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your songs have given some of us the strength to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't some vague memory of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but your desire to reach people with your music.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Expressing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your anger, your joy, your sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you started a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you sang at the school festival, why you came to Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you wanted to make a living from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so afraid of? Stop being a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in front of you is someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,who gained the strength to keep going thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who felt so much happiness just getting to sing with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who would have bet everything on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who believes in you and loves your music…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your excuse to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Move it!\N- Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, I'm going on ahead. Take the train back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be the one running.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You stayed true to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk to us, just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you started a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking forward to hearing you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any regrets, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're shooting for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday we'll prove to you that we weren't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And until then, we'll do everything we can to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we won't lose to you without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make you say that we were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll show you that we made the right choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone who just played like shit out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you sure run your mouth a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re an idol band.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any regrets,\nthen at least play the part properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Be professionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll be at the next festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Play like you did today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll be stealing every single one of your fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck is that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:20:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I still like you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m confessing my love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My fingers are static My fingers are trembling{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are no written answers Nor any stinging failures{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have always been who I am And I will remain who I was{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I fight There will be no tomorrow{\i0}
